TECHNICAL WRITER - OPERATIONS - Required for a leading OIL & GAS GROUP CO.-UAE ***CONTRACT HIRE***
Purpose and Scope
To review and update - Technical Concepts, IGD Operating Manuals, GOP, SI, OAG/IGD Manuals, TA, Verify P&ID;'s, Audit TAs, Prepare and maintain Procedure/Spade List/Spade Diagram for OAG & IGD.
Desired Candidate Profile
B.Sc. Degree or Higher Tehcnical qualification with 8 years of Oil & Gas industry experience - Must be familiar with the following :
To review and update - Technical Concepts, IGD Operating Manuals, GOP, SI, OAG/IGD Manuals, TA, Verify P&ID;'s, Audit TAs, Prepare and maintain Procedure/Spade List/Spade Diagram for OAG & IGD - HSE - CORAL DESIGN, ETC.
